        <h1 style="font-size: var(--fs-4xl);">Oregon Coast 101: Hug Point, Cape Meares, and why you slow down.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Highway 101 is not a shortcut. It's a 363-mile meditation at 45
          mph, punctuated by sea arches, lighthouse switchbacks, and the
          kind of sideways rain that makes people from everywhere else
          question their life choices. We love it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <figure class="article-hero">
